  Stable on amd64.

  01 Aug 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> kdebase-pam-6.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  30 Jul 2005; Gregorio Guidi <greg_g@gentoo.org> kdebase-pam-5.ebuild,
  kdebase-pam-6.ebuild:
  Stable on x86.

*kdebase-pam-6 (09 Jul 2005)

